snippet.title: Teller's Duty - Wishlist On Steam
snippet.description:
Work as a teller in Kertasia Bank, thanks to your distant uncle. In Teller's duty, you will face strict bank rules, difficult customers, and moral dilemmas as you save for your mother’s medical bills and dream business. Every decision shapes your future in this story-rich simulation of survival and ambition.

Wishlist On Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3428570/Tellers_Duty/
Music used: The Travelling Symphony by Savfk - www.youtube.com/@UCXlppUGWeGtHBp_1xKsawmQ
